title: How to be Productive Over the Summer
itunes:title: How to be Productive Over the Summer
description:
The Gals are giving you tips on how you can stay productive over your summer break? Yes it's fun to chill and take it easy, but it might also be the perfect time to work on that side hustle! Plus, who else is excited for this season of the Bachelorette!?

 You can check out our
channels on YouTube:

Danielle Carolan


Follow @galsonthegopodcast on Instagram to submit your own questions for next week’s episode, get involved, and more!

@daniellecarolan @brookemiccio Talk to you guys next Wednesday and for the next
episode!
